Class Track

java.lang.Object
com.jvn.musilog.data.Track
public class Track extends Object

  • Field Details

    • youTubeIdRegex

      private static final String youTubeIdRegex
      Regex pattern for a YouTube video ID. Google doesn't specify the format of these IDs, but reverse-engineering suggests that the format is modified Base64.
      See Also:
      • Constant Field Values

    • spotifyTrackUrlPattern

      private static final Pattern spotifyTrackUrlPattern
      Regex Pattern for a Spotify track URL. The format of the ID is Base62, as described in Spotify's documentation.
